\[
=\sum_{i_{a}}\sum_{n_{a}}M_{i_{a}i_{a+1}}^{*n_{a+1}}\left(\sum_{j_{a}}C_{i_{a}j_{a}}^{m_{a}n_{a}}M_{j_{a}j_{a+1}}^{n_{a+1}}\right)
\]

\end_inset

We continue this iteration until we reach 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{i_{b-1}j_{b-1}}^{m_{a}n_{a}}$
\end_inset

