\]

\end_inset

As usual we can define
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L_{i_{1}^{A}w_{1}^{A}j_{1}^{A}}^{[1]}=\sum_{n_{1}^{A}m_{1}^{A}}A_{1,i_{1}^{A}}^{\dagger[1]m_{1}^{A}}W_{1w_{1}^{A}}^{m_{1}^{A}n_{1}^{A}}A_{1,j_{1}^{A}}^{[1]n_{1}^{A}}
\]

